org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.task

Class TaskLauncherInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.task.TaskLauncherInitializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TaskLauncherInitializer
extends Object
implements Serializable
    TaskLauncherInitializer is used to initialize the task launcher.
    It contains every information that can be used by the launcher. It's a kind of contract so that each launcher must use its required information coming from this class.
    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 1.0
    See Also:
